verbose_text: Firstly, the correlation matrix was computed in order to discriminate the variables, thus selecting 10 parameters (acetoin, 2,3 butanediol, ethanol, ethyl acetate, titratable and volatile acidity, glycerol, reducing sugars, phenylethyl alcohol and isoamyl alcohols).
evidence: glycerol, reducing sugars, phenylethyl alcohol and isoamyl alcohols
